column2: This task consists of updating the RTEMS References Wiki page according to the instructions given in the RTEMS GoogleCodeInProjects Wiki page for the year 2012 and page 1. You will need to request a user account on the wiki and be careful to avoid making updates that conflict or delete other relevant citations. You will upload a text file containing the entries that you added to the wiki page. We have constructed the Google Scholar search for this task for your convenience.
